data.description:
$3000/mth unfurnished & $4000/mth furnished with utilities. This is a beautiful craftsman-style home in the historic Summerville neighborhood with a massive front porch! Once you open the front door it is like a story full of southern charm. Downstairs is a large living room with wood-coffered ceilings and a custom brick fireplace. You also have a spacious dining room with wood coffered ceilings and a fireplace, an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, shaker-style white cabinets, and granite. Your Master Suite is on the main level and is complete with an updated bath with plenty of space. There is a second bedroom downstairs that is accessible from both the hallway and the Master Suite which makes for a perfect bedroom for small children. Head up the original wooden staircase and arrive at a huge open family room with a sitting area and kitchenette. Upstairs has an additional 3 bedrooms and 1 updated bathroom. The backyard is fenced in which makes for a perfect place for kids to play and pets to run around. We would love to give you a tour of the home!

Rent is $3000/mth unfurnished & no utilities included. Rent is $4000/mth furnished with utilities included. If furnished, we include a Masters Clause in the lease which states that we rent out the entire house for the tournament. This means that you will need to find another place to stay during that week. The benefit is that we will give you a large deduction in rent for April. This is negotiable if you're willing to pay a higher monthly rental price. No smoking inside the house. Well-behaved pets are allowed.
